Package: scMetaTraj
Type: Package
Title: Metabolic State Space and Trajectory Analysis for Single-Cell Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Jinwei", "Dai",
           email = "greg0453@163.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description:
    scMetaTraj provides a framework for modeling cellular metabolic states
    and continuous metabolic trajectories from single-cell RNA-seq data
    using pathway-level scoring. The package enables lineage-restricted
    metabolic analysis, metabolic pseudotime inference, module-level trend
    analysis, and visualization of metabolic state transitions.
